            "title": "伊朗揚言攻擊全球觀光景點 鎖定美以敵對官員",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"伊朗揚言攻擊全球觀光景點 鎖定美以敵對官員\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fv_I.XkTtoyQQZcfeIuV_Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/9d183650-24bb-11f1-bcbf-75ac64d5ff5d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">伊朗揚言攻擊全球觀光景點 鎖定美以敵對官員</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
